<i>noun</i>: 도박, 賭博 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>도박, 賭博</dt><br>
<dd>the act of playing for stakes in the hope of winning (including the payment of a price for a chance to win a prize)</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: gambling, play, gaming</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
